ok time to get serious i know u guys are just itching to know waht china is like... umm well its different like everyone uses the bud or taxis. i swear ive already been in like 10 different taxis.  i dont know if u could say it means everyones poor its just i think they spend their money in different ways.  for instance everyone here (i hate to admit) dresses cooler.  theyre more formal sometimes but in a cool way.  like they have awesome dressy style im jealous of. the best part are the skirts and shoes. everyone is dressed nice all the time.  another thing is the  hair. its liek dye madness here.  some for worse but mostly for the better. there are stores lining the streets like literally sometimes u can go for a mile down a street and see only stores and restaurants. 

i guess when im home ill reflect some more btu these are the biggest differences.

ok for all u guys that dont know... its still pretty cool. today was the only semi ok day so a cause my moms friends are boring but nice.  I GOT MY HAIR DYED!! its liek darkish brown with subtle highlights and a little trim.  the hairdresser dude was all like  want to cut ur hair because its so heavy...blah blah i know thats nothin special but i thought he was funny cause he wasnt gay or anything and he did a good job.  he didnt know i was from the US and thought iw as jsut deaf or something because i didnt talk to anyone.  i got the cutest shoes! i want to like take pics and show u guys!! one pair is white and pink with a flower and the other are so hot theyre like 4 inches and black and shiny yay.

hot skirt too..

ok guys thats all im gonna write for today... if i dont write anything for a while rest assured i want to!!! i miss everyone!!

the ideal boyfriend
 

 
. /// his appearance ... 
. // what color is his hair? dark
. // what color are his eyes? green/brown
. // how tall is he? very tall
. // is he thin or muscular? haha thin... i think its kinda pitiful and cute
. // does he have long or short hair? longish... shaggy anyway
. // is he pale or tanned? sickly pale.. nono it doesnt matter
. // what does he like to wear? clothes...as long as hes not gangster anything else is fine 
. // does he wear make up? if he can pull it off awesome
. // your favorite body part on him would be? hair/eyes
. /// his personality ... 
. // is he quiet and shy or loud and outgoing? a lil of both would be nice
. // is he independent or dependent? mostly independent 
. // is he aggressive or passive aggressive? hehe
. // is he distant or affectionate? well DUH!
. // is he funny or serious? really funny
. // is he lazy or energetic? ehh all guys are lazy its their nature
. // is he intelligent or dumb? niether 
. // is he optimistic or pessimistic? a lil pessimistic... sarcasm is good too
. /// does he ... 
. // does he play an instrument (if so, what)? guitar!!/drums!!/bass!!...anything band related
. // does he play a sport (if so, what)? ehh soccer or hockey
. // does he do anything artisitc (if so, what)? draws/writes/anything is cool  i like the artsy types
. // does he write (if so, what)? songs??
. // does he do drugs, drink, smoke etc? it doesnt really matter as long as its not who he is
. // does he abuse himself (cut, burn, etc) or is suicidal? ewww no
. // does he always seem to be on the bad side with the law? occasionally
. // does he get along with his parents (and your parents)? doesnt really matter but they kinda have to be super nice to mine 
. // does he believe in god? itd be nice yeah
. // does he believe in extra celestial beings? ehh i dunno im not into it
. // does he go to school? ya 
. // does he work (if so, where)? hmMm movies or something
. // does he color in or out of the lines? prob out... but id make him color in cause im such the perfectionist 
. // does he have many friends? sure 
. // does he have many friends that are girls? sure 
. /// would he ... 
. // would he hold your hand everywhere you go? aww...
. // would he cuddle with you every chance he gets? sweetness 
. // would he display affection in public places? why not
. // would he pay your bus fare? i wish 
.// would he stick close to you in crowded rooms? def 
. // would he surprise you for no occasion what so ever? aww!!! 
. // would he stop whatever he was doing just to see you? thatd be nice 
. // would he randomly tell you he loves you in the most inappropriate sit? teehhee
. // would he start arguments with you or stop(prevent) them? doesnt matter as long as i win 
. // would he play with YOUR hair when he is nervous? if he wants?? lol 
. // would he kiss the tip of your nose hinting that he wants a kiss? haha sure that seems uhh normal? 
. // would he buy you flowers? only gardenias
. // ... or would he buy you chocolate? yayy!!
. // would he comment on other girls while with you? hehe
. // ... or would he act like you were the only girl for him? thatd be super nice but isnt that a given?
. /// what would he do if ... 
. // ... you were sad? make me laugh
. // ... you were mad? pretend it wasnt him but admit it if i threaten to kick his ass
. // ... you were to break up with him? if i really wanted to then i want it to be mutual 
. // ... you wanted to take a break? take the freakin break! but be willing to go back out
. // ... you were to move away? *gulp*
. // ... he forgot your birthday? dude thatd be the end
. // ... he accidentally insulted you? haha let me insult him back
. /// on a first date he would ... 
... take you to a movie? if he wants
... take you dinner? yayy
... take you to a concert or show? the best choice of course but i wouldnt make him
... take you to a comic convention? YES!
... take you to a game? those are fun sure
... or take you to a (?) doesnt matter even if we walk around aimlessly and just hang out
... respect you? haha it depends...kidding  
... value what you have to say? umm i think
... pay for everything? if hes rich
... buy you a gift? doesnt have to
... walk you to your door? doesnt have to
